        django-subcommand2
        ==================
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/django-subcommand2.svg
            :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/django-subcommand2
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/dm/django-subcommand2.svg
